        title: 'How can I contact the team if I face any issue during the application process?',
        description:
          'Shoot a quick mail at <b>info@kolpokoushol.org</b> and we hope to get back to you at the earliest!',
      },
      {
        title: 'How do I stay updated on the deadline, venue and post-application selection process?',
